{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775905518977,"sessionID":"ses_283c9a98fffehRYFFcueTbv47U","part":{"id":"prt_d7c37af60001qwxVJMYynA3f6c","messageID":"msg_d7c3782f1001X8X2uFbCioGKiy","sessionID":"ses_283c9a98fffehRYFFcueTbv47U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-719b2442717a4bb8a3b66a61076a398c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: sidebar_position: 1\n3: id: installation\n4: title: Installation\n5: description: Install AgentCube and set up your development environment\n6: ---\n7: \n8: # Installation\n9: \n10: ## Prerequisites\n11: \n12: Before installing AgentCube, ensure you have the following prerequisites:\n13: \n14: ### System Requirements\n15: \n16: - **Operating System**: Linux, macOS, or Windows with WSL2\n17: - **Kubernetes**: v1.24+ cluster (minikube, kind, or production cluster)\n18: - **kubectl**: v1.24+ configured to access your cluster\n19: - **Helm**: v3.8+ (optional, for Helm deployment)\n20: \n21: ### Language-specific Requirements\n22: \n23: For Python SDK:\n24: - Python 3.8+\n25: - pip package manager\n26: \n27: For Go client:\n28: - Go 1.19+\n29: - Go modules enabled\n30: \n31: ### Kubernetes Setup\n32: \n33: Verify your Kubernetes cluster is running:\n34: \n35: ```bash\n36: kubectl cluster-info\n37: kubectl get nodes\n38: ```\n39: \n40: Ensure you have sufficient resources:\n41: - Minimum 2 CPU cores\n42: - 4GB RAM available\n43: - 10GB disk space for sandbox pods\n44: \n45: ## Installation Methods\n46: \n47: ### Option 1: Helm Chart (Recommended)\n48: \n49: Install AgentCube using the official Helm chart:\n50: \n51: ```bash\n52: # Add AgentCube Helm repository\n53: helm repo add agentcube https://volcano-sh.github.io/agentcube/charts\n54: helm repo update\n55: \n56: # Install AgentCube\n57: helm install agentcube agentcube/agentcube \\\n58:   --namespace agentcube-system \\\n59:   --create-namespace \\\n60:   --set image.tag=v0.2.0\n61: ```\n62: \n63: Verify the installation:\n64: \n65: ```bash\n66: kubectl get pods -n agentcube-system\n67: ```\n68: \n69: Expected output:\n70: ```\n71: NAME                         READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE\n72: agentcube-controller-0       1/1     Running   0          2m\n73: agentcube-router-0           1/1     Running   0          2m\n74: ```\n75: \n76: ### Option 2:kubectl Deployment\n77: \n78: Deploy directly using kubectl:\n79: \n80: ```bash\n81: # Apply CRDs\n82: kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/main/manifests/crds.yaml\n83: \n84: # Deploy AgentCube components\n85: kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/main/manifests/deployment.yaml \\\n86:   -n agentcube-system\n87: ```\n88: \n89: ### Option 3: Development Build\n90: \n91: For development or testing unreleased features:\n92: \n93: ```bash\n94: # Clone the repository\n95: git clone https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube.git\n96: cd agentcube\n97: \n98: # Build the agentcube binary\n99: make build\n100: \n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 312. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nsidebar_position: 1\nid: installation\ntitle: Installation\ndescription: Install AgentCube and set up your development environment\n---\n\n# Installation\n\n## Prerequisites\n\nBefore installing AgentCube, ensure you have the following prerequisites:\n\n### System Requirements\n\n- **Operating System**: Linux, macOS, or Windows with WSL2\n- **Kubernetes**: v1.24+ cluster (minikube, kind, or production cluster)\n- **kubectl**: v1.24+ configured to access your cluster\n- **Helm**: v3.8+ (optional, for Helm deployment)\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md","time":{"start":1775905518956,"end":1775905518976}}}}
